        "The crosstab reveals a much more detailed picture than the single ARI score alone. Clusters 0, 1, and 2 are essentially perfect, corresponding almost entirely to COAD, KIRC, and PRAD respectively — K-means separated these three cancer types cleanly using gene expression alone. Cluster 3 is also largely clean, made up almost entirely of BRCA patients (247 of 250).\n",
